				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: A few hints for bazaar trading<a name="54716"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Aug 2 04 3:22 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Don't always try to undercut your competition, because you could seriously mess up item prices and really jip yourself in the long haul.
<br />

<br />
Don't worry about whether or not the item is lore, you have 7 LORE slots at your disposal.
<br />

<br />
Don't lower your asking price every 10 minutes, let it sit their for a while.
<br />

<br />
Do sell high.
<br />

<br />
Do research items but don't make rash decisions just because you're being undercut.   
<br />

<br />
</span></td>
